    {
        "content": "<p>Looking quickly, I don't think that <code>outParam</code> is the issue here. Indeed <code>h</code> in your final <code>example</code> does not match the corresponding argument to <code>lift_mkQ</code> unless we commit some minor defeq abuse and use that <code>id a = a</code>. The <code>rw</code> tactic will not commit this sin; the <code>erw</code> will but is usually a sign something you be doing things differently earlier on.</p>",
